flowchart TD
    A([User Request]) --> B[Validate Session and Input]
    B --> C{Request Type}

    C -->|Login| D[Authenticate User]
    C -->|Data Actions| E[Run Business Logic]
    C -->|Forgot or Reset Password| F[Token Flow and Email]
    C -->|File Upload| G[Validate and Store File]

    D --> H[(Database)]
    E --> H
    F --> H
    G --> I[(File Storage)]

    H --> J[Build Response]
    I --> J
    J --> K([Success or Error to User])
